To generate the messages file use:
pybabel extract -F translation/babel.cfg -o translation/messages.pot translation

To create a PO for some language:
pybabel init -i translation/messages.pot -d translation/translations -l pt_BR

To compile the translations for use:
pybabel compile -d translations

To create a new messages file when the strings change:
pybabel update -i translations/messages.pot -d translations
